    About Jivox IQ Platform

    Welcome to the Jivox IQ platform.

    Jivox IQ is a data-driven dynamic advertising platform that you can use to create and serve personalized digital ads. You can use Jivox IQ to:

    1. Design or import externally designed creatives.
    2. Define and evaluate rules based on data that comes from disparate sources.
    3. Serve personalized ads to the user, dynamically selecting and optimizing creative assets at runtime, based on the data, rules, and performance.
    4. Monitor running campaigns to view performance metrics at a granular level.

    You can set up personalized ad campaigns in Jivox IQ using data from a diverse range of sources: Jivox cookies, data management platforms (DMPs), demand side platforms (DSPs), geographic data, weather data, time, date, day, social media, or any custom data that is accessible via a web API.

    If you are new to Jivox, refer to the following topics to get started:

    • Learn about Ads
    • Learn About Tag Generation
    • Learn about Reports

    You can also watch the following short video for an overview of Jivox IQ:
